    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a lot to take in. i was also reading some stuff about how these regs might actually help the industry long-term by pushing for cleaner tech and preventing environmental damage that costs money later. do you think there's any real economic benefit to these rules, or is it all just extra cost for the owners?",
